 The Royal African Young Leaders Forum returns for its second edition, Spiritual Father of the Yoruba race, His Majesty, Arole Oodua Olofin Adimula, Ooni Adeyeye Enitan Ogunwusi, OJAJA II honored exceptional young Africans, on Saturday, 29th of May, 2021 at The Oduduwa Hall, Obafemi Awolowo University. This year’s edition of the Royal African Young Leaders Forum Awards was tagged; “Africa of the Future, Unlocking the Hidden Treasures of our Continent”. A total of 100 outstanding young Nigerians were celebrated and inducted as Members of The Royal Court of the Kingdom of Ife on this special occasion.  Among the 100 exceptional Young Nigerians that where honored is our very own Tosin Ajibade, CEO of Olorisupergal Media, Olamilekan Bamidele, Oluwaseun Ayodeji Osowobi, Popoola Doyin David, Kunle Adewale, and many others.